such as this place:

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:04.340
the tiny city of Gibraltar on the southern coast of Spain.

00:04:04.340 --> 00:04:08.860
Famous for its rock, 
its monkeys, and for causing diplomatic
tension between the United Kingdom and Spain.

00:04:08.860 --> 00:04:10.900
But what about the Falkland Islands:
which caused so much tension

00:04:10.900 --> 00:04:13.820
between the United Kingdom and Argentina, that they went to war over them.

00:04:13.820 --> 00:04:17.580
These places belong in the last group of Crown properties known as: British Overseas Territories,

00:04:17.580 --> 00:04:20.340
but their former name,
'Crown Colonies,' gives away their origin.

00:04:20.340 --> 00:04:23.120
They are the last vestiges of the British Empire.
Unlike the Commonwealth Realm,

00:04:23.120 --> 00:04:26.300
they have not become independent nations and continue to rely on the United Kingdom

00:04:26.300 --> 00:04:28.420
for military and, sometimes, economic assistance.

00:04:28.420 --> 00:04:31.700
Like the Crown Dependencies, everyone born within their borders is a British citizen.

00:04:31.700 --> 00:04:33.740
The Crown Colonies are,
in decreasing order of population:

00:04:33.740 --> 00:04:38.460
Bermuda, the Cayman Islands, the Turks and Caicos Islands, Gibraltar, the British Virgin Islands, 
Akrotiri and Dhekelia, Anguilla,

00:04:38.460 --> 00:04:43.940
Saint Helena, the Ascension Islands, Tristan da Cunha, Montserrat, the British Indian Ocean Territory,
the South Georgia and South Sandwich Islands,

00:04:43.940 --> 00:04:47.200
the Falkland Islands, the British Antarctic Territory,
and the Pitcairn Islands.

00:04:47.200 --> 00:04:48.200
For our final Venn diagram:

00:04:48.200 --> 00:04:52.640
the United Kingdom is a country situated
on the British Isles and is part of the Crown,
which is controlled by the Monarchy.

00:04:52.640 --> 00:04:55.300
Also part of the Crown and the British Isles are the Crown Dependencies.

00:04:55.300 --> 00:04:58.920
The independent nations of the former Empire that still recognize the Crown are the Commonwealth Realm,

00:04:58.920 --> 00:05:03.160
and the non-independent remnants of the former Empire and are the British Overseas Territories.

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.120
Thank you very much for watching!

